    "name": "Bunny Hop Hop",
    "steam_appid": 3292830,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292830/extras/ae954673bffa821966d4d88df3ffdae2.avif?t=1765307381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292830/extras_big/ae954673bffa821966d4d88df3ffdae2.avif?t=1765307381 width=800 height=237 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bunny Hop Hop</strong> is a super cute and energetic game where you play as Bunny the rabbit, on a mission to help clear the sky of a strange, spreading pollution.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump from cube to cube to color them and clean up the sky. Once all the cubes are ready, make them explode and escape to the next area. <strong>But be careful!</strong> The pollution has started to affect the local creatures. Evil foxes, angry hail, and wild monkeys will try to stop you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292830/extras/e08bf136ef17e3ccc972e533e72840cd.poster.avif?t=1765307381\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292830/extras/e08bf136ef17e3ccc972e533e72840cd.webm?t=1765307381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Luckily, you're not alone. You can collect carrots and playful weapons to help you along the way. Some clouds are your friends, and they’ll help you reach safety when things get tough.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292830/extras/61f6a90495edd9fa7af80ca73a26dde2.poster.avif?t=1765307381\" width=600 height=317 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292830/extras/61f6a90495edd9fa7af80ca73a26dde2.webm?t=1765307381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s a colorful, chaotic arcade-style adventure where every level brings you closer to restoring the skies and saving a world that’s still full of hope and cuteness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single Player</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 levels to unlock</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Biomes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Console control, keyboard or mouse Input (Steam Deck being verified!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand-drawn assets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local Score feature</p></li></ul>",
